    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Hand saws set in a deep U-shaped frame with a thin blade, which is slightly wider than the blade of a fretsaw; especially suited to cutting curves.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
